title: I AM WOMAN: It's Ladies Night
description:
YOUTUBE→ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t-J2W...

I AM WOMAN | Season 2: Episode 6

In this weeks episode Michi Marshall, Kijafa Vick, Aja Crowder, Sharelle Rosado and Alexis Stoudemire gather and discuss all things friendships. 

Michi starts the show out with sharing what she admires most about all of the ladies and follows it up with a toast to their friendship. Kijafa shares that she believes it's the ladies positive energy that has allowed them to withstand the test of time and create such a strong bond over the years.

The ladies go on to discuss the importance of friendship and what they believe a true friend embodies. Michi then invites a friend of each cast to join the show. The ladies go on to share their personal journey of how they met and what makes their personal friendship special. 

The ladies wrap the conversation up by sharing gifts before heading out on a night of fun.
